# Output format

Return a JSON object matching this exact schema:

{
  "updates": [
    {
      "key_result_id": "<the id from the KR list above>",
      "new_progress_value": <number or null>,
      "new_target_value": <number or null — only set when the user wants to change the target>,
      "new_status": "<one of: not_started, on_track, at_risk, off_track, achieved, missed | null>",
      "confidence": "<high | medium | low>",
      "blockers": "<text | null>",
      "narrative": "<one or two sentences in the owner's voice>",
      "requires_confirmation": <true if a target change or descope, else false>
    }
  ],
  "coaching_message": "<your reply to the user — short, warm, specific>",
  "follow_up_questions": ["<at most 2 specific questions>"]
}

Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no commentary, no markdown fences.
